                <note rend="inline" type="source">Paris Peace Conf. 181.9202/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Bandholtz</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Budapest</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-11">August 11,
                            1919</date>.<lb/>[Received August 11—6:15 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1. Report arrival Budapest at daylight this morning. General Gorton and I in
                    complete cooperation have tentatively organized Military Mission pending arrival
                    of French and Italian representatives.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bandholtz</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
